      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiwch pahrzelt Kalnus \nus zittu Weetu/ ka to ne warr \noumanniht / ko wiwch eekſch fa- \nwas Duſmibas apgahſch. "
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiwch kustina to Sem- \nmi no ſawas Weetas/ ka win- \nnas Pamatti triöfe. "
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiwch paweht Saulei/ \ntad ta ne uslezz/ wiwch ais- \nspeesch Sehgeli preekſch Swaigſ- \nnehm. "
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiwch weens isplatta \ntahs Debbetis/ un staiga us teem \nInhras Angſtumeem. "
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiwch darra tohs Wah- \ngus/ to Orijonu un Sectizu/ \nun tahs aptlehtpas Swaigſnes \nprett Deenas-Widdu. "
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiwch darra leelas Lee- \ntas/ ko ne warr iswaizaht / un \nBrihanmus/ ko ne warr isſkai- \ntiht. "
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redſi/ wiwch eet man \nfezzen/ ka es to ne redſu/ wiwch \npawebrtahs/ ka es to ne famanu. "
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Raugi/ kad wiwch ais- \ngrabbj/ kas to atkat atneſtihs? \nkas fazzihs us winnu: Ko dar- \nri tu? "
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiwch irr Deews/ fatwu \nDuſnibu wiwch ne nowehrſch / \nappakſch to tohp paſemmott tee \nlepni Baitgi. "
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zik maſki es winnam \natbildexhn/ un iſtaifſchn mauus \nWahdus prett winnu? "
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jepſchu es arrt taiſns \nbuhtu/ tatschu es ne warreischu \natbildexht/ bet man buhs jawu \nSohgi veeluhtgt. "
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jepſchu es fauzu / un \nwiwch man atbild/ tatschu es ne \nwarru tizzeht / ka tas mannu \nBalsi dsird. "
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo wiwch itt ka ar Weh- \ntru manni ſagrausch/ un padar. \nra man dauds Wahtes bes Wai- \nnas. "
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiwch ne kanj mannam \nGarram atspirgtees/bet pee-ehti- \nna manni ar Ruhktumeem. "
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja ar Spehku (kas ja \ndarra)/ redſi/ tad irr wiwch \nwarrens / un ja Teefä janahk/ \nkas mans Leczinceks buhs? "
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja es pats tatfnojoſs/ \ntad manna Mutte manni pasud- \ndina/ bubſchu es skaio-firdigs/ \ntad wiwch tatschu manni par \npawehrtitu isfaufs. "
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Etmu es uenoſeedſigs/ \ntatschu es fawu Dsihwibu ne ee- \nzeentju / man reebjahs dsihwoht. "
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weena weentga Leeta irr/ \nkadeht es etmu fazzijs : Wiwch \nir to Nenoſeedſigu ir to Bes- \ndeewign nomatta. "
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja wiwch schaufch/ tad \nonahwe wiwch ahtri/ wiwch ap- \nfineij to Nenoſeedſigu Kahrdina- \nschanas. "
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta Gemmetobp ta Bes- \ndeewiga Rohka dohta/ tas ap- \nkahj winnas Teetas-Kungu \nWatgus. Woj tas ta ne irr? \nkas tad to darra? "
    }
  ],
